# SYNOPSIS
#
#   AX_ENABLE_SSL()
#
# DESCRIPTION
#
#   Add a feature named ssl, which is enabled by default on all platforms but Windows.
#   If enabled, uses `AX_CHECK_OPENSSL` to set the `LDFLAGS`, `LIBS` and `CPPFLAGS`,
#   as well as defining `USE_OPENSSL` inside `config.h`
